fields.title: Request for Trauma Assessment Tool
fields.description: We need a specialized assessment tool for trauma-related symptoms in adolescents. Current tools don't adequately address this age group's specific needs.
fields.justification: Recent research shows that adolescent trauma responses differ significantly from adult patterns. A specialized tool would improve our diagnostic accuracy.
fields.target_population: Adolescents aged 13-17 with suspected trauma history
fields.expected_outcomes: Better identification of trauma symptoms, improved treatment planning, reduced misdiagnosis rates

fields.title: Modify GAD-7 for Youth Population
fields.description: Request to modify the existing GAD-7 assessment to be more appropriate for youth aged 13-18.
fields.justification: The current GAD-7 uses language and scenarios that don't resonate with younger clients. Age-appropriate modifications would improve engagement and accuracy.
fields.expected_outcomes: Increased assessment completion rates, better client understanding, more accurate anxiety measurement
fields.admin_notes: Approved for development. Please work with clinical team on language modifications.

fields.title: Social Anxiety Assessment for Students
fields.description: Request for a new assessment specifically designed to measure social anxiety in academic settings.
fields.justification: Many students experience social anxiety specifically in school environments. A targeted assessment would help identify these issues more effectively.
fields.target_population: Students aged 14-22 experiencing social anxiety in academic settings
fields.expected_outcomes: Better identification of academic-related social anxiety, improved support strategies, enhanced student success rates
fields.admin_notes: Similar functionality already exists in current social anxiety assessments. Consider using existing tools with additional context questions.
